  "name": "RPlog_Bespin_Cultural_Festival",
  "title": "Grand Opening of the Bespin Cultural Festival",
  "summary": "At the Grand Opening of the first annual Bespin Cultural Festival, Baroness-Administrator Quinne Stardust Rose works the packed Yarith Hotel lobby, reuniting with the Quarren doctor Druze and the shy, kitbashing technician Selko, both of whom helped foil a recent bombing. Caspian Presav Crestian Tarasar arrives with his Trandoshan captain Drorq, trading dry banter and rubber-mask jokes, while the self-reliant Lynae joins the conversation over drinks. The party moves to the ballroom, where Quinne delivers a show-stopping musical number and welcomes the crowd before settling at her VIP table. There, amid fireworks, spice cigarettes, and gourmet food, the group swaps stories of Quinne's rise from club singer to city administrator, Selko's hardscrabble life aboard a Squib salvage fleet, and Crestian's tangled web of titles, before Quinne slips away to tend to business, leaving Selko a gift of Yarith pajamas.",
